__NAME__ purpose
restrict debug mode to requests comming from specific hosts
__END__

__NAME__ synopsis
<arg choice='plain' rep='repeat'><replaceable>IP_address_glob</replaceable></arg>
__END__

__NAME__ description
The &conf-DebugHost; configuration directive restricts
&glos-debug; mode to only selected list of client hosts.
</para><para>
DebugHost accepts a list of IP addresses and IP address ranges.
__END__

__NAME__ notes
See &glos-debug; glossary entry for complete discussion on using debug
mode.
__END__

__NAME__ example: enabling DebugHost
<programlisting>
DebugFile /tmp/debug

DebugHost 10.1.1.0/24 12.176.97.0/25 127.0.0.1
</programlisting>
__END__

__NAME__ see also
DebugFile, debug_qualify, DebugTemplate
__END__

